name: Multi Storey Car Parking Game
description:
Multi Storey Car Parking Game.
Multi level car parking is a new idea base game for racing car and parking from the showroom or car garage.Different from the others car parking game.Here you can select the car from the showroom by the help of left. Special left move the car from one floor to another floor to out going.When you move from the car by floor by floor and pick the path according to given condition and park in the parking area. From the parking Area you can move the car in the showroom. Beautiful environment an HD Graphics.Good control and multiple level car parking game..
Feature of Game.
Good control and smooth.
Drifting Effect.
High speed car.
Different camera view.
Multiple car model.
stunning HD Graphics.
